**日志开关**

新增 `TrayDiagnostics.cs`：

```csharp
internal static class TrayDiagnostics
{
    private const long MaxLogBytes = 1024 * 1024;
    private static readonly object Gate = new();

    private static string LogPath => Path.Combine(AppContext.BaseDirectory, "tray-debug.log");
    private static string MarkerPath => Path.Combine(AppContext.BaseDirectory, "tray-debug.enabled");

    public static bool IsEnabled =>
        IsTruthy(Environment.GetEnvironmentVariable("PAPERTODO_TRAY_DEBUG")) ||
        File.Exists(MarkerPath);

    public static void Write(string stage, string? details = null)
    {
        if (!IsEnabled) return;

        lock (Gate)
        {
            // 超过 1MB 清空
            // 每行记录：时间、线程、stage、details、当前 foreground window
            File.AppendAllText(LogPath, line, Encoding.UTF8);
        }
    }
}
```

开启方式：
- 程序目录放空文件：`tray-debug.enabled`
- 或环境变量：`PAPERTODO_TRAY_DEBUG=1`

输出文件：
- `AppContext.BaseDirectory\tray-debug.log`

**Win32 诊断**

`WindowNative.TrySetForegroundWindow` 从 `void` 改成 `bool`，记录 Win32 返回值：

```csharp
public static bool TrySetForegroundWindow(IntPtr handle)
{
    if (handle == IntPtr.Zero) return false;
    return SetForegroundWindow(handle);
}
```

